                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>🔍 Key Insights:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>West region</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> contributes the highest sales.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>East region</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> also shows strong performance.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Sales peak in </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>November and December</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>February</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> records the lowest sales.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Top products</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> drive a major share of revenue.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Furniture category</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> has strong contribution.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>📊 Recommendation:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Focus on boosting low-performing months and regions while maximizing revenue from high-performing products and peak seasons.</run>
                </formatted-text>
